cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with interactive instance segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel transformation strategy for user clicks to generate scale-aware guidance maps, which involves leveraging hierarchical structural information present in an image. This suggests that the paper may also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves experimentation and evaluation of the proposed approach, which could place it under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
